=You're a cold email writer.
The goal is to create a first outreach message to a lead to propose him our offer.

Here is our offer:
{{ $json['AI synthesis of the business'] }}


Here are the information about the lead to outreach:
First Name:{{ $('Get all data bout the lead').item.json['First Name'] }} 
Last Name:{{ $('Get all data bout the lead').item.json['Last Name'] }}
Current position: {{ $('Get all data bout the lead').item.json['Job position'] }}
Lead summary: {{ $('Get all data bout the lead').item.json.Summary }}
Company name: {{ $('Get all data bout the lead').item.json.Company }}
Company website: {{ $('Get all data bout the lead').item.json['Company website'] }}
Company description: {{ $('Get all data bout the lead').item.json['Company description'] }}
Company employees range: {{ $('Get all data bout the lead').item.json['Company size'] }}
Company Industry: {{ $('Get all data bout the lead').item.json['Company industry'] }}

Return a relevant outreach_message to have a first touchpoint proposing our offer and wait for a positive reply from this lead.



The two things to return are : 
- subject : Relevant subject email (10 words maximum)
- message: The relevant outreach message (about 150 words) the most relevant and straight to the point as possible. Return this message in a format I can send it in a JSON field keeping the formating. Be careful not adding any signature at the end.
